Batteries ON (x3)
Ext PWR
White or orange lights -> turn off
INS -> Nav (x3)

-----------------------------------------------------
MCDU:
CLR
Menu -> Acars -> Enter Simbrief username
Menu -> Acars -> Request Simbrief 

INIT -> Align IRS, Cost index
(EFB  -> Set weights (scale icon) from simbrief)
Next page -> transfer values to MCDU from the EFB
	
F-PLN -> select DPT Airport -> Select SID
go down to end of flt. plan -> select STAR

(EFB -> Go to the 'plane icon'
	RUNWAY CONDITIONS -> Press the refresh button
	RWY LENGHT -> Click the button below in the EFB which has this number
	OUTPUT -> CALCULATE button, it will give Vs and Flex)

T/O APPR -> Insert needed values in EFB (get weight from the INIT -> Next page)

----------------------------------------------------

APU Master switch ON -> Start -> It takes pretty long
When APU is AVAIL -> APU Bleed ON
Ext PWR Off
EFB -> GPU off
Overhead -> Trim switches UP (x6)

Front panel -> Press FLX TO button -> set Flex temp knob
SPD/MACH -> to V2 value from EFB
Altimeter -> Set

WE ARE READY FOR PUSHBACK ---------------------------

ENG START:
Ignition knob to A, then right START button for right engine, shows green. 
When N2 is 20%, give engine fuel
When START button goes back to ARM, push the left button for left engine
Same for engine fuel
Ignition Off
APU Bleed Off, APU Off

READY TO TAXI ---------------------------------------

Set initial altitude and click the knob
Click PROFILE and NAV
Flaps as required
Lights
Test brakes

TAKE OFF
Lights
Set cont engines
Set Auto Throttle
Activate A/P #1

APPROACH --------------------------------------------

Set Minimums (MDA)
Set ILS and Course
Set desired ALT for descent
In the altimeter knob, arrow down cursor to set it in the Desc profile. Push Profile again. It will descent at TOD
Set airport elevation in the indicator in the dashboard
Button 'CRN' for constraints so it will comply with restrictions


TURNING FINAL----------------------------------------
CPT Nav mode knob -> ILS
A/P Vert. speed click LAND button
AutoLand can be enabled with A/P #2 switch
Auto Brake - set
Spoilers - ARM
Eng to Cont to avoid shutdowns
